Hawan gaggawa na cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Hawan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna kamanceceniya a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA, kuma Burtaniya ta tabbatar da cewa yayin da yake cikin matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana haɓaka cikin sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa ya kamata su haɓaka shirye-shirye don karuwar masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kulawa ta lafiya da musamman kulawa mai ƙarfi.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton wani sabon kamuwa da cutar sankarar bargo, wanda ba a san asalin cutar ba, a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton wani sabon nau'in kwayar cutar coronavirus, wanda ke nufin kwayar cutar coronavirus 2 na cutar ta hanyar numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da kwayar SARS-CoV-2 an sanya mata sunan cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida a yanzu ita ce kashi 80% na waɗanda ke da COVID-19 suna da ƙananan cututtuka, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 na cutar, COVID-19 ta ci gaba zuwa mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar izinin asibiti, yayin da kashi 6% ke da mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mafi mahimmanci.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin karuwar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / EEA da Burtaniya, kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Burtaniya tare da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu karin mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya.
Bayan mamaye kasar Sin, cutar ta COVID-19 ta ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma annobar COVID-19 mai saurin yaduwa a duniya a halin yanzu tana bin hanyar China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
A cikin Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5th Edition, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, bisa ga bayanan WHO na cutar.
A cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an fara ba da rahoton tabbatar da shari'o'i uku da Faransa ta bayar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 ga mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU / EEA da Burtaniya, waɗanda a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, kuma a wannan ranar, sun kai adadin shari'o'in cutar 39,768, kuma an ba da rahoton mutuwar 1,727 daga cikinsu, 17,750 na kamuwa da cuta da 1,441 na mutuwa sun fito ne daga Italiya kadai.
Samun jimlar abubuwa da abubuwan da suka faru a matsayin ci gaba na adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19.
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin adadin COVID-19 da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da kuma Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da duk waɗannan bayanan don kimanta cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU / EEA, da kuma Burtaniya, kuma an kwatanta duk waɗannan bayanan da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakilcin masu cutar COVID-19 masu aiki, mun ƙididdige jerin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 waɗanda suka daidaita zuwa kwanaki 14, la'akari da yanayin yanayin cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya, a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa da aka ruwaito a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya
A cikin yanayin yanayin COVID-19 wanda ya faru a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya, ya bi hanyar yanayin a lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
Ga Tarayyar Turai/EEA da kuma Burtaniya baki ɗaya, abubuwan da suka faru a matsayin barkewar cutar COVID-19 sun fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan suka ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma kasashen Turai/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar a cikin yanayin COVID-19.
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimillar adadin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Rahoton ya nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, sauran kasashe 15 na Tarayyar Turai / EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton ƙananan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar, idan aka kwatanta da adadin waɗanda ke Italiya, wanda ya kasance makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin cututtukan COVID-19 da aka ruwaito sun yi saurin ƙaruwa a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Abubuwan da aka lura a cikin yanayin COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta ci gaba da haɓaka cikin ƙimar kusan a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Wannan ya bambanta da ƙasashe da ke cikin matakai daban-daban, canje-canje a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da ma'anar shari'a daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe, da kuma al'ada daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya don gwaji don tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, gami da gwaji.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da aka fi fama da cutar a Italiya sun ba da rahoton halin da ake ciki a yankin cewa kashi 10% na masu fama da COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci, kuma kafofin watsa labarai da yawa sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai mahimmanci a yankunan suna aiki da iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan karbar COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (bayanai ba a nuna su ba).
Koyaya, yakamata a tattara su azaman tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin lamuran da aka ruwaito da adadin mutuwar.
Nazarin da aka gudanar a cikin 2010-11 ya nuna babban canji a cikin damar bayar da kulawa mai mahimmanci da matsakaitan gado a Turai, wanda ya fara daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 gadaje a cikin mutane 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu da yawa ko ƙasa da Italiya (a matsakaici 12.5 wuraren kulawa da gadajen kulawa a kowace mutane 100,000 a cikin 2010-11).
An ba da yanayin samfurin da ya shafi rashin iyawar kiwon lafiya a cikin sabon sabon ƙididdigar haɗarin COVID-19 na ECDC na shida, tare da kimantawa ga ƙasashen EU / EEA da Burtaniya cewa yawan masu karɓar COVID-19 suna da haɗarin wuce gona da iri na asibiti &gt; 90%.
Saboda yawancin shari'o'in sun kasance a wasu yankuna a cikin ƙasashen Turai, Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa galibi suna ba da sabis ne kawai ga yawan jama'ar yankin da aka ƙayyade, saboda haka ya kamata a ba da bayanin shari'o'in da kuma kulawar kulawa a kan yankin na yanki na 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewa daga Italiya da kuma halin yanzu a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 ta duniya tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/EEA da Burtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa ya kamata su kasance a shirye don sabon yanayin watsawa na SARS-CoV-2 mai yuwuwar cutar coronavirus da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman da kulawa mai mahimmanci, kamar yadda lamarin yake faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda sabon Binciken Hadarin Cikin Gida na ECDC ya nuna, hanzarin amsawa, daidaitacce, da kuma cikakke hanya na da mahimmanci wajen jinkirta yaduwar cutar SARS-COV-2-ta hanyar sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa ragewa, yayin da saurin karuwar adadin shari'o'i na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da amsawa yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
