A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa duk wuraren shakatawa kamar shaguna da wuraren motsa jiki dole ne su zama na gaggawa, kuma ta yi alƙawarin biyan ma'aikata albashi har zuwa kashi 80 cikin ɗari zuwa iyakar £ 2500 a wata don hana rashin aikin yi a lokacin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya ba da sanarwar tsauraran matakan nuna bambancin zamantakewar jama'a, ta hanyar hana taron mutane sama da biyu, da kuma hana tafiye-tafiye da ayyukan waje da ake ɗauka da mahimmanci.
Ba kamar matakan da suka gabata ba, 'yan sanda sun karfafa wannan matakin ta hanyar sanar da tarar da tarurruka.
"An umarci yawancin kasuwancin su rufe, sai dai kasuwancin da aka ɗauka ""mai mahimmanci"" sun haɗa da manyan kantuna, asibitoci, bankuna, shagunan kwamfuta, tashoshin mai da tashar jirgin sama".
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an tabbatar da farkon cutar COVID-19 a cikin jihar Pacific ta Arewa maso Yammacin Washington, wanda ya faru ne a kan wani mutum da ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu.
An kafa rundunar yaki da cutar korona ta fadar White House a ranar 29 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya kuma ta sanya takunkumin shiga ga matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, babbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka, ta sanar da cewa sun kirkiro na'urar gwajin kanta.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta fara jinkirin gwajin da ya ɓoye ainihin yanayin barkewar cutar a lokacin.
Gwajin ya lalace ne ta hanyar gwajin cutar da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga kayan aikin gwaji na gwamnati (ta masana'antu, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen watan Fabrairu, da kuma tsauraran sharudda ga mutanen da suka cancanci yin gwajin har zuwa farkon Maris (ana neman umarnin likita daga baya).
Har zuwa ranar 27 ga Fabrairu, jaridar The Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
Har zuwa 13 ga Maris, yankunan Atlantika sun ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaji ƙasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya ruwaito cewa, "Mutane da dama suna da alamun cutar, kuma likitocin sun jira sa'o'i ko kwanaki don yin gwaji".Bayan an samu rahoton mutuwar farko a Amurka a Washington a ranar 29 ga watan Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci, kuma sauran jihohi sun bi wannan matakin nan take.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke karatun su a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe.A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, an ba da shawarar Amurka ta yi kimantawa game da tasirin sabon coronavirus a cikin ƙasar ta hanyar ƙungiyar masana cututtuka a Imperial College London.
A wannan ranar, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Amincewa da Shirye-shiryen Cutar Korona, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 na kudade ga hukumomin tarayya don magance barkewar cutar.
Kamfanoni sun sanya takunkumin hana ma'aikata tafiya, sun soke tarurruka, kuma sun karfafa ma'aikata suyi aiki daga gida.
An soke wasanni da abubuwan da suka faru na yanayi. A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye na kwanaki 30 ga yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, tare da tsawon watanni 13.
Kashegari, ya fadada iyakancewar zuwa Birtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci ta kasa, wanda ya ba da damar kasafin kudin tarayya ya amsa matsalar.
Farawa a ranar 15 ga Maris, kamfanoni da yawa sun rufe ko rage lokutan aiki a duk faɗin Amurka don ƙoƙarin rage yaduwar kwayar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da cutar a cikin jihohi 50 da Gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa New York City tana da mutane 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar fiye da adadin waɗanda ke Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, magajin garin ya ce, ana ganin an fara aikin kwantar da hankula yayin da kimar masu kamuwa da cutar ta ninka daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a New York City, inda aka samu mutum 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar, kuma mutane 672 suka mutu sakamakon cutar. A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta tabbatar da cewa ita ce kasar da ta fi kowacce kasar kamuwa da cutar a duniya, bayan da ta hada da China da Italiya.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaba Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idojin sa ido kan zamantakewar al'umma har zuwa ranar 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan ranar ne jirgin USNS Comfort, asibitin jirgin ruwa mai gado 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
