A New York, an samu sama da mutum 100,000 da suka kamu da cutar a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki Fadar White House saboda mayar da martani kan barazanar da kuma sarrafa saƙonnin kai tsaye daga ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya don shirya jawabai na jama'a da kuma wallafe-wallafe game da cutar tare da Mataimakin Shugaban Kasa Mike Pence.
Tallafin da aka samu game da yadda Trump ya magance matsalar ya rabu biyu a cikin masu ra'ayin mazan jiya.
Jami'an Amurka da wasu masu sharhi sun soki Amurka kan dogaro da shigo da kayan masarufi, ciki har da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da ake bukata daga China.
An yi amfani da nazarin tsarin tafiye-tafiye na iska don tsarawa da kuma duba yanayin yaduwar cutar kuma an buga shi a cikin mujallar Likita ta Balaguro a tsakiyar watan Janairun 2020.
