An gudanar da binciken lafiyar kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu masu bayyanar cututtukan coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
'Yan Afirka ta Kudu ne kawai suka gwada ba su da cutar da aka yi wa kwayar cutar.
Sakamakon gwajin ya kori dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, ciki har da matukan jirgin sama, ma'aikatan jirgin sama, jami'an 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin ayyukan jin kai, wadanda ke da matukar muhimmanci, duk sun kasance a karkashin sa ido da rashin lissafi na kwanaki 14 a cibiyar watsa labarai ta Wassara.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, Amurka ta fara janye wasu dakarunta daga Iraki saboda yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Sin ta tabbatar da cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Rasha, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da agaji zuwa China.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen isar da kayan agaji ga bangarorin da cutar ta addabi a kasar Sin, tare da karin kungiyoyin agaji a yankin Chicago da ke bayar da rahoton cewa sun kai kayan agaji na N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) don tallafawa kokarin bincike kan allurar rigakafi da magani tare da kare mutane masu fama da cutar a Afirka da kudu maso gabashin Asiya.
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Interaksyon ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da kayan rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da kayan rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar 'yan kwaminis ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura dala miliyan 2.26 na tallafi zuwa kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska na zinare miliyan daya zuwa yankin Wuhan, Turkiyya ta ba da kayan aikin likita cikin gaggawa, Rasha ta aika da tan 13 na kayan aikin likita zuwa yankin Wuhan, Malaysia ta ba da gudummawar takunkumin likita miliyan 18 zuwa China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin likita da suka hada da kayan rufe fuska 10,000, Amurka ta ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita 17.8 ton, kuma ta yi alkawarin samar da ƙarin dala miliyan 100 na ruwa don tallafawa waɗanda ke fama da cutar daga China bayan an kai su kasar Sin.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyaki da kwararrun likitoci don taimakawa Italiya wajen shawo kan barkewar cutar coronavirus.
Mai siyar da kaya Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwajin gwaji miliyan 1.1, abin rufe fuska miliyan 6 da kayan kariya 60,000 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha don rarraba ta Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, masks 100,000 da kuma famfunan iska 5 zuwa Panama.
Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta kuma ba da gudummawar kayan aikin likita ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da China ta yi.
Misali, Spain ta yanke kayan gwajin cutar coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi da kasar Sin, wadanda suke da kashi 30 cikin 100 na daidaito, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da 600,000 na takunkumin zinare na kasar Sin.
Belgium ta tattara kayan kwalliyar 100,000 da ake ganin sun fito ne daga China amma a zahiri daga Colombia.
A gefe guda, an sami karbuwa sosai a taimakon da China ke bayarwa a sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga watan Mayu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da wani aikin gaggawa na tallafawa kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin China ke yi na sarrafawa da kuma shawo kan annobar.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin ɓoye-ɓoye da suka hana hana hanawa da sarrafawa, da kuma halin da ake ciki yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ke ba da sabuntawa akai-akai don kauce wa rikicewa kafin bikin Sabuwar Shekarar Sin.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa yayin da ba ainihin shawarar da WHO ta bayar ba, amma kuma muhimmin nuni ne na jajircewa don magance cutar a wuraren da cutar ta fi yawa, kuma ya kira cutar "ba a taɓa ganin irinta ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a".
Darakta-janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC na da hadarin yaduwa a duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
"A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye -tafiye, Tedros ya tabbatar da cewa ""babu wani dalili na matakan da ke hana balaguron balaguro da kasuwancin ƙasa da ƙasa"" kuma cewa ""WHO ba ta ba da shawarar ƙuntatawa da ƙaura ba"."
"A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da dala miliyan 675 domin samar da kudade ga shirye-shiryen dabaru a kasashe masu karamin karfi, tare da nuna gaggawa wajen tallafawa kasashen da ba su da hanyar gano wadanda suka kamu da cutar, duk da yadda ta bulla".
"Tedros ya kara da cewa, ""dukkanin al'ummai idan akwai wani mai rauni, ya zama mai rauni ga kowa"," kuma ya bukaci al'umma ta duniya da ""su saka hannun jari a yau, ba za su yi asara ba daga baya"."A wani taron manema labarai na ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta ba da sunan cutar COVID-19".
A wannan ranar Tedros ya tabbatar da cewa Sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince da ba da ikon dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a cikin martani.
"An kafa ƙungiyar kula da rikice-rikicen Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda hakan zai ba da damar daidaitawa na amsawar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO za ta ba da damar mayar da hankali kan amsar lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya kawo ƙwarewarsu don tallafawa zamantakewar tattalin arziki da tasirin tasirin barkewar cutar"."
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kafa wani kwamitin horar da ma'aikatan WHO tare da kasar Sin don samar da kwararru na kasa da kasa da na WHO game da halin da ake ciki a kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen kula da cutar a yankin da kuma tantance "taurin cutar da kuma yiwuwar yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar kafa bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin kasa da gudanar da ziyarar kai tsaye don fahimtar tasirin matakan mayar da martani a larduna da yankuna, gami da birane da karkara. A ranar 25 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa duniya ta kamata ta dauki matakai masu yawa don shirya annobar cutar ta kwayar cutar, inda ta yi kira ga dukkan kasashe da su kasance cikin shiri cikin gaggawa.
"A cikin martani ga yaduwar barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da wata hadin gwiwa zuwa can don kimanta halin da ake ciki.A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a kara kimanta barazanar cutar coronavirus a duniya daga" sosai ", wanda shine mafi girman matakin tsaro da kimantawa.
Mike Ryan, daraktan shirin gaggawa na WHO, ya tuna a cikin wata sanarwa cewa: "Wannan shi ne abin da ya kamata gwamnatoci a duniya su sani: Ku farka.
"Wannan kwayar cuta na iya kasancewa a kan hanyarsa, don haka ya kamata ku kasance cikin shiri, kuna mai cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimakawa duniya ta guji mafi munin sakamako".
"Ryan ya kara da cewa ba a tabbatar da bayanan na yanzu ba don jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a su ayyana barkewar cutar a duniya, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar za ta nuna cewa ""mun amince da cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da kwayar cutar""".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris ne Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da barkewar annobar cutar coronavirus.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO ta damu matuka game da matakin gaggawa na yaduwar cutar da kuma tsananin rashin daukar matakan. WHO ta fuskanci kakkausar suka saboda rashin isasshen maganin cutar, gami da bayyana gaggawa na gaggawa ga lafiyar jama'a da kuma sanya cutar a matsayin annoba.
Amsar ta hada da umarni ga Tedros Adhanom, babban jami'in WHO, don neman ya yi murabus daga mukaminsa, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, dubun-dubatar masana 'yancin dan adam na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun jaddada girmama hakkin kowane mutum a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kwararru sun ce kowa na da hakkin ya yi aikin ceto, kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin wadata ko inshorar lafiya ba za a iya ɗauka a matsayin hujja ta nuna bambanci ga kowane rukuni ba.
Kungiyar ta ce kowa na da hakkin samun lafiya, ciki har da nakasassu, wadanda ke cikin 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, wadanda aka tilasta musu yin hijira a kan iyakoki, marasa gida da ke rayuwa a cikin mawuyacin hali, wadanda ke cikin tsare, da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin mutane da ba a tabbatar da sunansu ba da ke bukatar taimakon gwamnati.
Kungiyoyin kasa da kasa suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar cutar COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kirkiro wata hanyar samar da cikakken bayani kan yadda ake daukar matakan siyasa a kasashe daban-daban a duniya, da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari.
Ta hanyar inganta tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya, don magance tasirin kulle-kulle da ƙuntatawa kan tafiye-tafiye, Cibiyar Dijital, gami da shirye-shiryen bin diddigin manufofin ƙasa, da nufin taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen martani na duniya ga ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin China ta fuskanci suka daga Amurka, Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Michael Gove da Eduardo Bolsonaro, dan shugaban kasar Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, saboda yadda suka magance annobar da ta barke a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Wasu hukumomin lardin na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) sun samu cikas a yadda suke gudanar da aikin killacewa a yankin tsakiyar kasar Sin, wanda ke nuna rashin jin dadin yadda aka mayar da martani ga barkewar cutar a wadannan yankuna.
Wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa an yi wannan ne don kare sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin Xi Jinping daga fushin jama'a kan barkewar cutar.
Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian, sun yi watsi da amincewar da aka yi a baya game da barkewar cutar da ta fara a birnin Wuhan, amma sun goyi bayan ka'idar cewa cutar COVID-19 ta samo asali ne daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka karkashin Donald Trump ta yiwa cutar korona lakabi da "kwayar cutar Sin" ko kuma "kwayar Wuhan", inda ta ce "tashin hankalin kasar Sin kan cutar da ta zama annoba ta duniya" an soki irin wannan furucin da nuna wariyar launin fata da kuma nuna rashin nasarar gwamnatinsa wajen shawo kan cutar".
Jaridar Daily Beast ta samu wani sabon siginar sadarwa na gwamnatin Amurka da ke nuna cewa akwai wata matsala ta sadarwa da ke da tushe a cikin kwamitin tsaron kasa, inda aka yi da'awar cewa duk game da China ne.
Ya ce ya kamata mu yi kokarin isar da wannan sakon ta kowace hanya da za mu iya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma fitowar talabijin. Jaridu kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin da China ke yi na kai agaji ga kasashen da ke fama da cutar wani bangare ne na yunkurin daukar matakin hukuntawa ga duniya baki daya.
"Shugaban manufofin kasashen waje na EU Josep Borrell ya yi aiki don tunatar da cewa akwai abubuwan da ke haifar da siyasa, ciki har da matsalolin tasiri ta hanyar canji da 'siyasa ta alheri.'"
Borrel ya kuma ce, "Ba kamar Amurka ba, China ta yi wa'azin cewa ita ce ta yi rashin gaskiya kuma abokin tarayya ne mai aminci".
China ta kuma bukaci Amurka da ta janye takunkumin da ta kakaba kan Syria da Venezuela da kuma Iran, yayin da ake zargin ta tura taimakon ga kasashen biyu.
