Kwayar ACE2 tana ɗauke da N-terminal peptidase M2 domain da kuma mai aikawa da acid a cikin tsarin C-threonine.
ACE2 hanya ce ta farko ta hanyar kwayar halitta, wanda enzyme dinsa ke aiki kai tsaye a jikin kwayoyin hanta da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
An cire ƙarin kwayar ACE2 daga cikin kwayar ta hanyar wani enzyme da ake kira shades, kuma an fitar da sinadarin da aka narke zuwa cikin jini kuma daga ƙarshe an fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin kwayoyin: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na nau'in II, hanta, ƙwayoyin ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin jini, da ƙwayoyin endothelial, da ƙwayoyin tsoka na ƙwayoyin jini a yawancin kwayoyin.
ACE2 mRNA kuma yana cikin kwayar halitta na striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwayar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine yin aiki a matsayin mai daidaita daidaituwa ga ACE.
ACE tana tsallake hormone na antioxidant I zuwa antioxidant II.
ACE2 yana raba amino acid na carboxyl-terminal amino daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ya raba shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya kashe wasu peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 yana taimakawa wajen daidaita matakan watsawa na SLC6A19 da kuma masu karɓar amino acid da aka nuna a cikin cutar Hartnup.
Saboda wannan kwayar halitta ta wuce ACE2 tana taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin kwayar halitta ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta masu yaduwa, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar SARS) da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar COVID-19).
